claim.claim-text:
10. A method of playing a game using a gaming device comprising: 
(A) placing a wager on the gaming device; 
(B) starting the game; 
(C) generating a game outcome; 
(D) displaying an image on a display having a plurality of changeable sections, a fractional image being displayed in each of the changeable sections; 
(E) displaying a whole image on the display when a game wining outcome is generated; 
(F) displaying a non-whole image on the display when a game losing outcome is generated; and 
(G) paying a payout based upon the game outcome.
